= SDL_ClearError =
Use this function to clear any previous error message.


== Syntax ==
```c++
void SDL_ClearError(void)
```

== Code Examples ==
```c++
if (strlen(SDL_GetError()) != 0) {
  printf("SDL_Error : %s\n", SDL_GetError());
  SDL_ClearError();
}
```

